Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:06.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來 人們就對妖怪心存畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:12.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而走在那眾妖之前 統領著百鬼夜行的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:16.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們稱其為妖怪的總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是如此稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:21.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魑魅魍魎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:23.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑頭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉章就跟我年輕時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:04.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想憑藉「畏」成為妖怪之主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:09.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與被稱為「七人同行」的妖怪一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「七人同行」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:17.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個叫犬神的幹部非常危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:24.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個能利用憎恨來增加自己力量的可怕妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:31.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現在陸生眼前的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:35.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱神刑部狸玉章與其部下七人同行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:42.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們公然向奴良組和陸生宣戰 搶奪奴良組的地盤 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了稱霸全國 開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:48.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:59.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去我曾混入了人類社會並拼命模仿人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:02.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛成為妖怪不久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:18.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就過著不被人認同 不被人接受的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:24.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我 還不知道有妖怪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:30.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時天下之大卻沒有我的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:32.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:48.44,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,300)}開幕於黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好恨 我好恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨死奴良陸生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…他的頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:31.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:36.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣把你們解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神廉貞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神改造 人式一體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花開院流陰陽術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉送葬水包槍 柚羅MAX
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電燈換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:15.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我們回講堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經映射出妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妖怪萬一真的出現了的話那該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:26.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:31.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有這破魔七枝刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:49.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我不會偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:00.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:02.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:14.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 雕蟲小技
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這些絲線就想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:23.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:28.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我的線纏住的話越掙扎就纏得越緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首無的線可是很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:48.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 我知道了妖怪也有著像人類一樣的社會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能成為我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你也是妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:58.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同…同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻為何要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要讓我有這般遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:20.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想見識見識你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎麼不去死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:33.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱小的妖怪沒有生存的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:39.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正活下去也只會被人類蔑視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回到那裡去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:42.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:08:00.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想變強大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:36.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨越強烈 力量就越強大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著來 我讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適合你的新的妖怪世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:05.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉章把既不是人類也不是妖怪的我看作是真正的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:09.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉章 四國妖怪之主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:15.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有玉章才會身懷真「畏」成為妖怪之主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的才幹與你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:22.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你那樣只想做個平凡的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:28.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就算是人類也是個引人注意的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:32.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還用他的力量駕馭了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:38.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟成天被小心呵護著 還得意洋洋的你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被玉章騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我被騙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:53.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉章是一隻能夠若無其事地披著羊皮的狡詐狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 玉章也告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:10.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪在人類上位 我有力量 天下還有我的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:13.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這觀點是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:16.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類與妖怪是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:44.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被憤怒驅使而真正覺醒的犬神是無法阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:57.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界上只有玉章一個人認同我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他說的都是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這下糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:16.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會認同你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:21.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認同像你這樣的被人尊敬的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 我的線可沒這麼容易斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 請退後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:05.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是玉章忠實的僕人 妖怪犬神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直完全不工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:33.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講堂那邊很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:42.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學 你去看看發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要修理這個放映機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:48.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 就會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:12:59.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡被破損了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:22.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學 出現了出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 真的出現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:30.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 講堂裡有只大妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生大人 請退後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首無
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟變得這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭歸位了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門打不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學 島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:37.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被混泥土困住了 這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護陸生大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:51.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:53.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會盡力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:57.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱小的妖怪就得死 這是四國妖怪的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 請快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:09.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學 島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:41.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒人能來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:22.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺死奴良陸生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:45.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味著落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:17.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該你下臺了 你這丑角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 少主沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是奴良陸生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你點陽光你就燦爛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:37.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰都無所謂 殺死你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:50.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是錯誤地認為體型越大就越厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:58.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 你怎麼會這麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:01.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認同 我絕不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:18.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學 講堂裡有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:21.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫給我吧 我有破魔七枝刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:33.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由身為清十字團團長的我去制裁妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:47.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:57.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:18.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不過是這種程度的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼上位下位 你器量真小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:51.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的半吊子妖怪要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:52.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:11.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟被你這種…被你這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:33.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 犬神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:38.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉章 我還沒輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:44.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我重要的同伴 我還不能讓你死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是奴良陸生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然是一表人才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:04.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已沒必要去騷擾人類了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟企圖著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:10.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:17.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會奪取你的「畏」 成為所有妖怪之主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:21.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的臺詞 小狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:25.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就到這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:30.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 下次相遇之時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:34.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會收下你的「畏」和生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱神刑部狸玉章
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛演戲的狸貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:48.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶犬的牙齒已被拔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:54.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與玉章的決戰已迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:29.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬頭 你也來買這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:32.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 《我所愛的奴良組》？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:34.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛鬼大人自費出版的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:37.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該賣不出去吧…賣不出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:38.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 滑頭鬼之孫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.99,0:23:41.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三七分的酒杯
